Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.26,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,I would like to show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.11,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,Cut open my skull
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.11,0:01:29.12,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,Look into my head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:30.46,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,I don’t
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:32.28,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,know why I’m so harsh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.95,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,I could be so brash
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.76,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,I’m going to clash
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:38.94,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,’cause I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:45.70,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,I can always show my everything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:49.87,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,If this moment was for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.98,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,I try to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:53.42,Op-jp,NTP,0,0,0,,Lend my ear
